n><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2525917\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 17, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104axy1665702717519.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/axy1665702717519.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/axy1665702717519.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"axy1665702717519\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"axy1665702717519__message_levelall_calls_to_global_objects_and_descriptors_491573\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">These messages record all calls for signatures (entity and component descriptors) and global objects.\n </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"axy1665702717519__note_N1001F_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This message level quickly builds a very large message frame.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"axy1665702717519__topic_d109567e1_d109568e1_d109569e1_d109570e1_d109571e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d112025e55\">Calls to UARs</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"axy1665702717519__p_d152021e1_d152022e1_d152023e1\">When calling for objects in a UAR, the messages show which UAR file is opened, which objects are obtained from which source, and which objects could not be found.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"axy1665702717519__p_d152024e1_d152025e1_d152026e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Object Lookup:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UAR</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Object size=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Size</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Type</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">@</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">@</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"axy1665702717519__p_d152027e1_d152028e1_d152029e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Object Lookup: d:/myapp/my_app.uar\nObject size=0000220 edc/customer@acme.edc\nObject Lookup: d:/uniface/common/usys/usys.uar\nObject NOTFOUND [0] prc/$$register@system_library.prc\nObject Lookup: d:/myapp/myapp_messages.uar\nObject size=0000032 msg/u_busy@myapp@usa.msg\n... </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"axy1665702717519__topic_d109572e1_d109573e1_d109574e1_d109575e1_d109576e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d112025e111\">Calls to Global Objects</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"axy1665702717519__p_d152033e1_d152034e1_d152035e1\">When calling for global objects, the message identifies the target object and shows where it was located:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"axy1665702717519__p_d152036e1_d152037e1_d152038e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Object size=:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Code</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, lang =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, lib =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, id =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Location</var>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Object Type Codes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\">Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Object type</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Panel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">D</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Device translation table</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Glyph</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">M</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Message, help text, or language setup</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">P</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Global ProcScript or global variable</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Keyboard translation table</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">U</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"axy1665702717519__table_d18323e1_d18324e1_d18325e1__entry__2\">Menu bar or menu item</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525917\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525917\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Message Level 128: All Calls to Global Objects and Descriptors Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 These messages record all calls for signatures (entity and component descriptors) and global objects. Note: This message level quickly builds a very large message frame. Calls to UARs When calling for objects in a UAR, the messages show which UAR file is opened, which objects are obtained from which source, and which objects could not be found. Object Lookup: UAR Object size= Size : Type / Name { @ Library @ Language } For example: Object Lookup: d:/myapp/my_app.uar Object size=0000220 edc/customer@acme.edc Object Lookup: d:/uniface/common/usys/usys.uar Object NOTFOUND [0] prc/$$register@system_library.prc Object Lookup: d:/myapp/myapp_messages.uar Object size=0000032 msg/u_busy@myapp@usa.msg ... Copy Calls to Global Objects When calling for global objects, the message identifies the target object and shows where it was located: Object size=: Code , lang = Language , lib = Library , id = Name ; Location . Table 1. Object Type Codes Code Object type C Panel D Device translation table I Glyph M Message, help text, or language setup P Global ProcScript or global variable T Keyboard translation table U Menu bar or menu item Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}